These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-1::.
Game: scrabble, monopoly, poker, snooker
Nationality: nigerian, australian, malaysian, mexican
1. Game:poker is between Nationality:malaysian and Nationality:australian##2
2. Game:snooker is on the left or right of Nationality:malaysian##3
3. Nationality:malaysian is not to the left of Nationality:malaysian##8
4. Nationality:australian != Game:poker##6
5. Game:poker is somewhere to the right of Game:scrabble##5
6. Game:scrabble is on the right of Nationality:nigerian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Game   | snooker  | scrabble | poker | monopoly  |
| Nationality   | nigerian | malaysian   | mexican  | australian |

