.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-2::.
House: modern, art-deco, gothic-revival, palace
Birthday: february, november, april, june
1. Birthday:june is not to the left of Birthday:june##8
2. House:modern is somewhere to the right of House:palace##5
3. House:modern == Birthday:november##1
4. House:palace is between House:modern and House:art-deco##2
5. House:art-deco is somewhere between House:gothic-revival and Birthday:february##7
6. Birthday:april is somewhere to the left of House:art-deco##5
7. Birthday:february is not to the left of Birthday:february##8

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |        2        |    3     |     4      |
| House   | gothic-revival | art-deco          | palace | modern     |
| Birthday    | april      | june | february | november |

