.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-3::.
Sport: parkour, rugby, baseball, climbing
Game: domino, poker, mah-jongg, snooker
1. Game:domino is not to the left of Sport:baseball##8
2. Game:poker is on the far left##1
3. Sport:rugby is on the right of Sport:parkour##1
4. Sport:rugby is in an even position##4
5. Sport:climbing is on the far left or far right##3
6. Sport:parkour is somewhere to the left of Game:snooker##5
7. Sport:climbing == Game:mah-jongg##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Sport           | parkour | rugby | baseball     | climbing |
| Game   | poker    | snooker   | domino | mah-jongg    |

